description: OREGON HIGH : A Climbing Guide to Nine Cascade Volcanoes. At last - the book Northwest mountaineers have been waiting for. Jeff Thomas, author of Oregon Rock, has written a comprehensive climber's guide ato Mt. Hood, Mt. Jefferson, Three Fingered Jack, Mt. Washington, North Sister, Middle Sister, South Sister, Broken Top, and Mt. Thielsen. This book includes complete route descriptions, six maps and over forty photographs, all designed to help you reach your summit. Published by Keep Climbing Press, Portland, Oregon.
